g\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120143TEGyLP7CmFtika32.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120145EFZGJeMD1SPbyUNT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120145YEnpcbHiBIzwdSo2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021312014768urHDpKJscEZoRb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120147qKWa8oTBXnrHuLMs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120150RbWFd6syDQSNm2u3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120151Gr9lSPJiMCpnVwtY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120151U1SMkF2BY94Gub0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120152fqD1Pnt6U0RLla2I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802131201525g8Kv132cGVMCHy9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>华盛顿特区史密斯国家肖像画廊正式发布了<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/art/barack-obama-official-portrait-michelle-unveiling-smithsonian-gallery-02-12-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">奥巴马和夫人米歇尔的官方肖像</a>。其中，奥巴马的肖像由 Kehinde Wiley 创作，米歇尔肖像的作者是 Amy Sherald。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120214fm51splecLrjBxYo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.465770\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120224oyrkx2Pn5XF61hD3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.199267\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>芬兰运动品牌 <a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/553048\" rel=\"nofollow\">KARHU 和去年末关店的 Colette 合作的鞋子</a>将于 2 月 23 日起登陆日本 BEAMS 原宿店发售。 </p><p>这双鞋以 Colette 的标志和芬兰国旗的蓝色为主要元素，售价 24000 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120323hRNqgwlJYOmXU7Vz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120336lgaH1xbNq3if65vO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120336uZh4Lm2Bi7nUKfx3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120332ysRJ8Q9PCTKo0Va5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120335IAEpKjqNDa1H3wg4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120335j84oWHPatil3pD0B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802131203383ziVSkXpy0GfJU7a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120340kNVl1ORtyp2gwqMm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120341O4zcUYJ9CSdRkDjl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2 月 16 日，前 Givenchy 设计总监 Riccardo Tisci 为 NikeLab 设计，以虚构的 NBA 篮球队<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/557664\" rel=\"nofollow\"> The Victorious Minotaurs </a>为主题的第二波单品即将在北美市场开售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802131204232NnFiKAfUxhBPYva.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180213120414Qjano1KsVqp2cb7I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021312041337mIcV2NPnqjSH0W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：KARHU</p>"}